        "Skill 3"
      ],
      "description": "In teamfights, first activate Mathilda's 1st skill,\nthen immediately use her 2nd Skill to get to a good position to initiate from\nand unleash her Ultimate on the primary target. This combo allows Mathilda to quickly CC a key enemy hero, and lets an ally follow up by using Guiding Wind from her 2nd Skill."
